text: Glykeria Gkatzogianni (; born 20 January 1987) is a Greek former footballer who played as a midfielder. She has been a member of the Greece women's national team. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Greek women's footballers Category:Greece women's international footballers Category:PAOK FC (women) players
